{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1>tips</h1>\n<h2>获取某个action的具体command</h2>\n<p>使用gui界面的keyboard shortcut 直接搜索 右键菜单中有 copy command id\n<a href=\"https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/getstarted/keybindings\">https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/getstarted/keybindings</a></p>\n<h2>task 相对路径</h2>\n<p>task.json 的<a href=\"https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/editor/tasks-appendix\">schema</a></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-json line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token comment\">// task.json</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"tasks\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">\"label\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"check-bot-client\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">\"type\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"shell\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">\"options\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n                <span class=\"token comment\">// 设置执行命令的相对路径</span>\n                <span class=\"token property\">\"cwd\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"bot-client-rust\"</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">\"command\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"cargo check\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">\"problemMatcher\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n                <span class=\"token property\">\"base\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"$rustc\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                <span class=\"token comment\">// 设置problemMatcher的相对路径</span>\n                <span class=\"token property\">\"fileLocation\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"relative\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">\"${workspaceRoot}/bot-client-rust\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/share/ide须知/vscode/"}}